"{\"uid\": \"click2houston.com-news-local-2024-06-12-houston-native-raevyn-rogers-aims-for-another-gold-medal-at-the-olympic-games-in-paris\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Keith Garvin, Anchor  Published:June 12, 2024 at 1:42 PM  Updated:June 12, 2024 at 9:37 PM  Recommended Videos  Keith Garvin, Anchor  She is a Houston girl who has made Houston very proud!\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 188, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 118, \"end\": 124, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jerry_Garvin\", \"score\": 0.9994989373989196, \"rank\": 0.0005013132674165113, \"text\": \"Garvin\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jerry_Garvin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jerry_Garvin\"}, {\"begin\": 143, \"end\": 150, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Houston\", \"score\": 0.9603335115851351, \"rank\": 0.04129531525496845, \"text\": \"Houston\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Houston\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Houston\"}, {\"begin\": 169, \"end\": 176, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Houston\", \"score\": 0.9603335115851351, \"rank\": 0.04129531525496845, \"text\": \"Houston\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Houston\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Houston\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Whether it was at the collegiate level, where she earned six national titles, or won a medal at the Tokyo Olympics, Raevyn Rogers has always run with her heart.\", \"from\": 190, \"to\": 350, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 306, \"end\": 319, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raevyn_Rogers\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Raevyn Rogers\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raevyn_Rogers\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raevyn_Rogers\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As she prepares to go for gold in Paris, KPRC2\\u2032s Keith Garvin spent time with her as she came home to be honored by the community she loves.\", \"from\": 351, \"to\": 491, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 385, \"end\": 390, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999999954899523, \"rank\": 4.510050565103324e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 406, \"end\": 412, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jerry_Garvin\", \"score\": 0.9994989373989196, \"rank\": 0.0005013132674165113, \"text\": \"Garvin\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jerry_Garvin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jerry_Garvin\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Rogers did the honors at the recent TSU Relays -- a track meet in which she still holds the record in the high school girls' 800-meter run.\", \"from\": 493, \"to\": 632, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Paris hopeful has run up an impressive resume' since her time at The Kinkaid School.\", \"from\": 633, \"to\": 721, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 637, \"end\": 642, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999999954899523, \"rank\": 4.510050565103324e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 702, \"end\": 720, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Kinkaid_School\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"The Kinkaid School\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3914\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Kinkaid_School\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Kinkaid_School\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This is an opportunity for me to come home and be with my community,\\\" Rogers said.\", \"from\": 723, \"to\": 806, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Obviously, TSU Relays is special to me.\", \"from\": 807, \"to\": 847, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 819, \"end\": 822, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Texas_Southern_University\", \"score\": 0.998941466471221, \"rank\": 0.000550958132332139, \"text\": \"TSU\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Texas_Southern_University\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Texas_Southern_University\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"TSU is where my grandparents met, so this is like family getting together for me.\\\"\", \"from\": 848, \"to\": 930, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 848, \"end\": 851, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Texas_Southern_University\", \"score\": 0.998941466471221, \"rank\": 0.000550958132332139, \"text\": \"TSU\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Texas_Southern_University\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Texas_Southern_University\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Raevyn's community came together during her Tokyo Olympic run in 2021.\", \"from\": 932, \"to\": 1002, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In what is referred to as \\\"the kick\\\" -- Raevyn came from almost last place in the women's 800-meter run, to cross the finish line with a bronze medal.\", \"from\": 1003, \"to\": 1153, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Coming off the curve, I just started thinking to myself, 'How many girls can I catch,'\\\" she recalled.\", \"from\": 1155, \"to\": 1257, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I remember literally being probably like at the 50 meters mark and thinking that I could get third place and a bronze would be nice because it was my mother's birthday.\", \"from\": 1258, \"to\": 1427, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So I went for it, and I am happy I did.\\\"\", \"from\": 1428, \"to\": 1468, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Raevyn is hoping to go for another medal at the Paris Games.\", \"from\": 1470, \"to\": 1530, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Her chance to advance comes in less than two weeks at the Olympic Trials at the University of Oregon in Eugene.\", \"from\": 1531, \"to\": 1642, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For Raevyn, it's a familiar setting.\", \"from\": 1643, \"to\": 1679, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It is where she won six national titles as a collegiate runner -- and is the first female Duck whose silhouette adorns a 10-story tower outside the track stadium.\", \"from\": 1680, \"to\": 1842, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As she trains for another shot at Olympic gold, Raevyn knows where her heart is.\", \"from\": 1844, \"to\": 1924, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's always going to be going for gold.\", \"from\": 1926, \"to\": 1966, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am going to always train hard and give my best,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 1967, \"to\": 2027, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am a winner.\", \"from\": 2028, \"to\": 2043, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am a champion.\\\"\", \"from\": 2044, \"to\": 2061, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can bet that Houston will be pulling for Raevyn in Paris and her tight-knit group of family and friends led by her mother Rhonda.\", \"from\": 2063, \"to\": 2196, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2080, \"end\": 2087, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Houston\", \"score\": 0.9603335115851351, \"rank\": 0.04129531525496845, \"text\": \"Houston\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Houston\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Houston\"}, {\"begin\": 2118, \"end\": 2123, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999999954899523, \"rank\": 4.510050565103324e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They call themselves \\\"Raevyn's Nest\\\" and many plan to root her on in Paris, but first from the track and field Olympic Trials in Oregon starting June 21.\", \"from\": 2197, \"to\": 2350, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2266, \"end\": 2271, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999999954899523, \"rank\": 4.510050565103324e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 2326, \"end\": 2332, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Oregon\", \"score\": 0.9999926967928535, \"rank\": 7.025912390055063e-06, \"text\": \"Oregon\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Oregon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Oregon\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"All finals will be airing live right here on KPRC2.\", \"from\": 2351, \"to\": 2402, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Copyright 2024 by KPRC Click2Houston - All rights reserved.\", \"from\": 2404, \"to\": 2463, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Emmy Award-winning anchor, husband, dad, German Shepherd owner, Crossfitter, Game of Thrones junkie, chupacabra hunter.\", \"from\": 2465, \"to\": 2584, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2506, \"end\": 2521, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/German_Shepherd\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"German Shepherd\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/German_Shepherd\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/German_Shepherd\"}, {\"begin\": 2506, \"end\": 2521, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/German_Shepherd\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"German Shepherd\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/German_Shepherd\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/German_Shepherd\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"email  facebook  twitter  instagram  \\u25b60:45  \\u25b61:04  \\u25b61:31  \\u25b61:32  \\u25b60:39  \\u25